00:15:27,125 --> 00:15:29,375
I want to perfect the
"Angel's Maneuver."

249
00:15:29,458 --> 00:15:31,583
I want us to become true stars.

250
00:15:31,666 --> 00:15:33,541
Then the people
who see us perform,

251
00:15:33,625 --> 00:15:38,000
the audience, other performers,
their hearts will become one.

252
00:15:38,083 --> 00:15:42,291
Even if they are not related.
They'll be just like family.

253
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:47,166
The "Angel's Maneuver" is a
way to become a "True Star."

254
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:49,583
At the time I thought
she was just talking

255
00:15:49,666 --> 00:15:51,416
like a silly little girl.

256
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:54,291
But somewhere along
the way I began thinking

257
00:15:54,375 --> 00:15:58,291
that I wanted to bring a
"True Star" into the world.

258
00:15:58,375 --> 00:16:01,333
"Only a demon can
raise an angel."

259
00:16:01,416 --> 00:16:03,875
I remembered someone
from a circus troupe

260
00:16:03,958 --> 00:16:06,750
I was in a long time
ago saying that.

261
00:16:06,833 --> 00:16:09,791
As we aimed to perfect
the "Angel's Maneuver,"

262
00:16:09,875 --> 00:16:14,125
I had no choice but to make
my special training more cruel.

263
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:17,541
That special training...

264
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:23,125
It's the same as that
special training I did

265
00:16:23,208 --> 00:16:25,291
before the circus festival.

266
00:16:32,625 --> 00:16:33,750
Sophie...

267
00:16:33,833 --> 00:16:36,041
What's wrong with you?!

268
00:16:36,125 --> 00:16:39,375
You'll never do a perfect
"Angel's Maneuver" like that!

269
00:16:45,875 --> 00:16:47,708
You're both really
going to leave?

270
00:16:47,791 --> 00:16:49,458
There is nothing more
we can learn from you.

271
00:16:49,541 --> 00:16:50,500
What?!

272
00:16:50,583 --> 00:16:52,791
I'll perfect the
"Angel's Maneuver."

273
00:16:52,875 --> 00:16:55,458
I'll make Sophie a "True Star."

274
00:16:55,541 --> 00:16:58,250
You're just a stepping
stone towards our goal.

275
00:16:58,333 --> 00:17:00,500
You think you can do it Leon?

276
00:17:00,583 --> 00:17:03,625
Do you really think
you can become a demon?

277
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:08,666
After a few years had
passed I heard a rumor

278
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,500
that Sophie had died.

279
00:17:11,583 --> 00:17:14,375
And that was it.
My dream was dead.

280
00:17:14,458 --> 00:17:16,958
To think he had
that kind of past.

281
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:18,708
Leon's special training...

282
00:17:18,791 --> 00:17:21,958
I thought it was just him
trying to break Sora's spirit.

283
00:17:22,041 --> 00:17:25,208
He really knew
what he was doing.

284
00:17:25,291 --> 00:17:27,833
So the "Angel's Maneuver"
is connected

285
00:17:27,916 --> 00:17:30,500
to becoming a "True Star"?

286
00:17:30,583 --> 00:17:34,500
No. The "True Star"
business is just a fantasy.

287
00:17:34,583 --> 00:17:36,375
It is impossible
to become a star

288
00:17:36,458 --> 00:17:38,958
without being hated or
resented by someone.

289
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:40,875
Everyone would be envious.

290
00:17:40,958 --> 00:17:45,250
Especially if you could perform
a "Perfect Angel's Maneuver."

291
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:49,500
You're wrong. I think
"True Stars" really can exist.

292
00:17:51,333 --> 00:17:53,375
Sophie thought the
"Angel's Maneuver"

293
00:17:53,458 --> 00:17:56,500
was the path to
becoming a "True Star."

294
00:17:56,583 --> 00:17:58,666
I believe that too.

295
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:02,333
I want you to teach me to do
a "Perfect Angel's Maneuver".

296
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:06,958
I don't believe in
such a thing anymore.

297
00:18:07,041 --> 00:18:09,125
I'd just drag you down.

298
00:18:09,208 --> 00:18:13,500
If we had met about three
years ago, then maybe I would.

299
00:18:15,375 --> 00:18:18,208
Rosetta? You want
to keep practicing?

300
00:18:18,291 --> 00:18:20,083
Uh, yeah.

301
00:18:20,166 --> 00:18:23,541
Alright. I won't bore you with
stories of the past anymore.

302
00:18:23,625 --> 00:18:26,375
Sora's eyes... They're
burning with a fire

303
00:18:26,458 --> 00:18:28,375
that I've never seen before.

304
00:18:28,458 --> 00:18:32,208
I've finally found the path to
becoming a true Kaleido Star.

305
00:18:32,291 --> 00:18:33,833
No matter how
much time it takes,

306
00:18:33,916 --> 00:18:35,750
I'm going to take that path.

307
00:18:35,833 --> 00:18:38,791
I will become a
true Kaleido Star!

308
00:18:38,875 --> 00:18:41,958
Imagine that you become
part of the trapeze.

309
00:18:42,041 --> 00:18:43,833
Don't go against the flow!

310
00:18:43,916 --> 00:18:46,125
How many times do
I have to tell you?

311
00:18:46,208 --> 00:18:49,083
Picture where the bars
will be three seconds ahead.

312
00:18:49,166 --> 00:18:51,208
Picture them three
seconds ahead.

313
00:18:56,291 --> 00:18:58,541
I did it!

314
00:18:58,625 --> 00:18:59,875
Don't get too excited.

315
00:18:59,958 --> 00:19:02,333
We're moving on to
the next step now.

316
00:19:06,333 --> 00:19:08,041
She is pretty good
on the trapeze.

317
00:19:08,125 --> 00:19:10,583
She's so much better,
in one day!

318
00:19:10,666 --> 00:19:11,583
--Cater!
--Pillar!

319
00:19:11,666 --> 00:19:13,125
Pillar!

320
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:23,083
Any villain who would
try to kill the princess

321
00:19:23,166 --> 00:19:24,666
will have to fight me first.

322
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:28,333
I accept your challenge.
Hahahahaha!

323
00:19:28,416 --> 00:19:31,541
I will fight. But why do I
always have to play the villain?

324
00:19:31,625 --> 00:19:33,666
Wow, awesome!

325
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:36,791
Say your prayers, evil queen!

326
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:39,125
You underestimate me!

327
00:19:43,166 --> 00:19:47,125
Sora's moves are much bigger
than they were in rehearsal.

328
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:49,791
She was like this
at the last show too.

329
00:19:49,875 --> 00:19:52,958
This isn't just being able to
make the audience smile.

330
00:19:53,041 --> 00:19:55,833
She's inspiring
everyone around her.

331
00:19:55,916 --> 00:19:59,458
And as another performer
it excites me somehow.

332
00:19:59,541 --> 00:20:02,041
This is Sora's true power.

333
00:20:07,541 --> 00:20:09,625
Southern Cross Illusion!

334
00:20:09,708 --> 00:20:11,916
Gigashock Explosion!

335
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:14,125
Infinity Tornado!

336
00:20:14,208 --> 00:20:16,291
Fantastic Firestorm!

337
00:20:16,375 --> 00:20:18,958
Four Thousand Legend
Cosmic Dream Spin!

338
00:20:19,041 --> 00:20:22,583
For someone who didn't wanna do
it, she's really into this show.

339
00:20:22,666 --> 00:20:26,708
Galactica Unbelievable
Splash Thunder!

340
00:20:27,708 --> 00:20:30,041
That girl's performance
is drawing out

341
00:20:30,125 --> 00:20:32,208
the other performer's charm.

342
00:20:34,375 --> 00:20:36,875
I have to defeat you,
we're running out of time!

343
00:20:38,291 --> 00:20:41,375
I don't wanna let you beat me,
but I'll do it... this time.

344
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:42,916
Fine.

345
00:20:55,333 --> 00:20:57,000
Don't remember
that in the script.

346
00:20:57,083 --> 00:20:59,500
I guess May's just
having fun in her own way.

347
00:20:59,583 --> 00:21:03,250
I won't forget what
you've done to me!

348
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:15,791
On the next one, Rosetta.

349
00:21:15,875 --> 00:21:17,333
Right!

350
00:21:26,791 --> 00:21:28,250
Good job!

351
00:21:43,708 --> 00:21:45,875
That's just what I'd
expect from you, Sora.

352
00:21:45,958 --> 00:21:47,208
You've easily bounced back

353
00:21:47,291 --> 00:21:50,666
from your depression after
the festival. Amazing.

354
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:53,583
Hm? I know that man...

355
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,833
--Hello.
--Hm?

356
00:21:56,916 --> 00:21:59,625
The performer who played
the prince is Sora Naegino.

357
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:01,666
She's pretty good,
don't you think?

358
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,625
Judging by your physique,
I'm guessing

359
00:22:03,708 --> 00:22:05,958
you're a trapeze
artiste as well.

360
00:22:06,041 --> 00:22:09,916
She certainly does have a
strange charm about her.

361
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,625
She could be the one to make

362
00:22:11,708 --> 00:22:14,666
that "True Star"
thing a reality.

363
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:17,083
I'm glad to know
you think so too.

364
00:22:17,166 --> 00:22:20,833
Hm? But wait,
I've seen you before.

365
00:22:20,916 --> 00:22:23,291
Why, you're...
you're Yuri Killian!

366
00:22:23,375 --> 00:22:25,166
Uh, yeah.

367
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:26,791
My instincts are telling me

368
00:22:26,875 --> 00:22:28,958
that Kaleido Stage
is up to something.

369
00:22:29,041 --> 00:22:32,208
I bet they're plotting
something big, eh?

370
00:22:32,291 --> 00:22:34,666
Well, that is a
possibility, sir.

371
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:40,416
I've finally decided the
path I'm going to take.

372
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:43,416
I'm going to master
the "Angel's Maneuver."

373
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,583
I know I can do it!

374
00:24:01,416 --> 00:24:04,333
I thought I'd give you a chance
to get your revenge, Leon.

375
00:24:04,416 --> 00:24:07,708
The Kaleido Stage
is reopening! But...

376
00:24:07,791 --> 00:24:10,125
The truth about what happened
between Leon and Yuri

377
00:24:10,208 --> 00:24:12,291
three years ago
will finally be revealed.

378
00:24:12,375 --> 00:24:15,666
The cruel demon who slashed
an angel's innocence to pieces.

379
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:18,416
That's enough, stop it you two!

380
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:23,750
Next time on Kaleido Star:
"The Amazing Fated Duel"!

381
00:24:23,833 --> 00:24:27,000
My wings are my dream
and on toward the sky.

